<p>After builders cleaning requires specialist tools designed to remove fine construction dust safely.</p>

<h2>HEPA Vacuum Systems</h2>
<p>These vacuums capture extremely fine particles such as plaster dust that standard household vacuums cannot filter effectively.</p>

<h2>Microfibre Cleaning Systems</h2>
<p>Microfibre cloths capture remaining dust particles during surface wiping.</p>

